whit.like <- function(d){
  g.d <- g^d
  sig2 <- (sum(g.d*per[1:m])/m)
  log.like <- m*log(sig2)-d*sum(log(g)) +m
  return(log.like)
}

(est <- optim(d0,whit.like,gr=NULL,method = "L-BFGS-B",hessian=TRUE,
                    lower=-100,upper=100,control = list(trace=1,REPORT=1)))
